{"_id":"8VlmxnFYGmaCAJsW","name":"Overdrive: Flowering Night","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/nature/plant-undersea-seaweed-glow-green.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the scene, Veil Breaches canʼt be opened, and whenever a foe is destroyed, create a <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>VOID BLOOM</strong></span> at its Speed. <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>VOID BLOOMS</strong></span> last until the end of the scene, count as Veil Breaches for friendly powers and abilities, and donʼt count for <strong>Incursion</strong>. Allies that end their turns Matched to one or more <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>VOID BLOOMS</strong></span> may clear 3 <strong>Drive Stress</strong>.</p>\n<p>Close all open Veil Breaches and create <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>VOID BLOOMS</strong></span> in their place now.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CFgozkC0JaVWIHlo","name":"Overdrive: The World","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/water/beam-ice-impact.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the scene, a foe of your choice gains <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>SEQUENCED</strong></span> at the start of your turn, and you no longer take additional <strong>Drive Stress</strong> for targeting multiple <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>SEQUENCED</strong></span> foes.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DV2wYjhuGj405pqi","name":"Overdrive: Fusion Cascade","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-explosion-yellow.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the scene, <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> deals 2 Harm instead of 1, and foes with <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> deal 2 Harm to other Matched foes when they explode. Apply <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RADIANCE</strong></span> to all foes within Speed 3 now.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Hg6TU78MrEGBkEHj","name":"Overdrive: Deadstar Venom","type":"section","img":"icons/skills/wounds/injury-triple-slash-bleed.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Choose a foe. Blink to Match them, then <strong>Prime</strong>, <strong>Lock</strong>, <strong>Weaken</strong>, <strong>Disrupt</strong>, and <strong>Fracture</strong> them until the end of the next round.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"V6UWuwheFUUk5ety","name":"Overdrive: Dead Zone","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-energy-light-white.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>You and all non-Boss foes of your choice within Speed 3 are removed from the encounter, reappearing in a silent, lightless void.</p>\n<p>While in the <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>DEAD ZONE</strong></span>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Characters are always Matched.</li>\n<li>All foes are permanently <strong>Weakened</strong> and <strong>Disrupted</strong>.</li>\n<li>Your <strong>Veilborn</strong> passive is always active.</li>\n<li>When you would take Impact, you take that much Drive Stress instead.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>DEAD ZONE</strong></span> lasts until you take any <strong>Drive Burn</strong>, or until all foes in it are destroyed.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"a7zTJajMqD7O6eRD","name":"Overdrive: Event Horizon","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/unholy/barrier-shield-glowing-pink.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the next 3 rounds (including the round you activate this), the effects of your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>GRAVITY WELL</strong></span> change to the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At the end of each of your turns, pull all foes within Speed 3 to Match you, then <strong>Lock</strong> all Matched foes. If a foe is already <strong>Locked</strong>, <strong>Stun</strong> them.</li>\n<li>Allies within Speed 3 gain +2 <strong>Weight</strong>.</li>\n<li>Your <strong>Speed</strong> canʼt change for any reason.</li>\n</ul>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dMsZ8qBBxLYrOHrd","name":"Overdrive: Starpiercer","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/unholy/beam-impact-purple.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>Your next attack with a Ranged Weapon rolls <strong>double</strong> dice and is an <strong>automatic Crit</strong>. For each 6 you roll, increase the Harm dealt by +1 (before multipliers).</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"k7epvRvmz750xqrE","name":"Overdrive: 3-Body Problem","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/defensive/illusion-evasion-echo-purple.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the encounter, you gain a second <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>QUANTUM DOUBLE</strong></span>, which materializes at a Speed of your choice. When a Power or ability references your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>QUANTUM DOUBLE</strong></span>, you may choose either (but not both).</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ltVMRz3ic3HNFB1L","name":"Overdrive: Hypergiant Mode","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/earth/barrier-lava-stone-orange.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the of rest the scene, whenever you end your turn in <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span>, Matched foes take 3 Harm. Whenever you destroy a foe, you may extend the duration of <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span> by 1 round.</p>\n<p>Enter <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>RED GIANT STANCE</strong></span> now, until the end of your next turn.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"o4ZIQtRs8rPNlAZY","name":"Overdrive: Perfect Flow","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-teal.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the encounter, your <strong>Accel</strong> becomes 8, you canʼt be <strong>Locked</strong>, <strong>Slowed</strong>, or prevented from <strong>Boosting</strong> in any way, and whenever you use a power, gain 1 <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>FLOW</strong></span>.&nbsp;</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pmLDzFoTZbUGFjER","name":"Overdrive: Baryon Symmetry","type":"section","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-deflect-teal.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the encounter, your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>ANTIMATTER SHELLS</strong></span> donʼt expire when they detonate. All allies without an <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>ANTIMATTER SHELL</strong></span> gain one now.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sTWVhziuREqxy3db","name":"Overdrive: Equinox Ward","type":"section","img":"icons/skills/trades/academics-astronomy-navigation-blue.webp","data":{"useResource":false,"resource":{"name":"","value":""},"description":"<p>For the rest of the scene, you can use your action to activate your <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>EQUINOX WARD</strong></span>. While active:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Youʼre permanently <strong>Locked</strong>, and gain 3 <strong>Inertia</strong> at the start of your turn.</li>\n<li>Matched allies deal +2 Harm with all weapons, and gain full <strong>Inertia</strong> from your <strong>Equilibrium</strong> passive instead of half.</li>\n<li>Attacks and powers from foes that arenʼt Matched to you have their Impact reduced by 2 and donʼt apply <strong>Statuses</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can deactivate <span class=\"infinite-revolution-highlight\"><strong>EQUINOX WARD</strong></span> at any time. Activate it now.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qOtwCyvq008f3Tyg":3},"flags":{}}
